column2: select top # s.specObjId, s.bestObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z_person, s.class_person, s.comments_person, s.class, s.subClass from wise_xmatch as xm  join SpecObjAll as s on xm.sdss_objid = s.bestObjID  join PhotoObjAll as p on xm.sdss_objid = p.objID  join emissionLinesPort as e on s.specObjID = e.specObjID  join wise_allsky as w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr where xm.match_dist<=# and s.zwarning=# and e.z># and e.zerr/e.z<=# and e.z<=# and w.w1cc_map=# and w.w2cc_map=# and w.w3cc_map=# and w.w4cc_map=# and w.ph_qual_det1<># and w.ph_qual_det1<># and w.ph_qual_det1<># and w.ph_qual_det2<># and w.ph_qual_det2<># and w.ph_qual_det2<># and w.ph_qual_det3<># and w.ph_qual_det3<># and w.ph_qual_det3<># and w.ph_qual_det4<># and w.ph_qual_det4<># and w.ph_qual_det4<>#
